com.ontotext.kim.model
Interface DictionaryFeeder

public interface DictionaryFeeder

This interface allows for an external implementation to feed Entity data into the KIMGazetteer's Dictionary.

Author:
danko@sirma.bg

Method Detail

init

void init(Map<String,String> keyValuePairs)
This method allows for the KIMGazetteer to pass custom specific configuration data to the feeder implementation. This data will be provided as additional configuration parameter for the KIMGazetteer plug-in. The the gazetteer will pass it to the DictionaryFeeder implementation at initialization time.

Parameters:
keyValuePairs - - a map of key and value string couples. This set of parameters will be interpreted only by the DictionaryFeeder implementation.

feedAll

void feedAll(DictionaryFeeder.EntityListener entListener)
This method will be used by the KIMGazetteer to fill its main fixed dictionary at start-up. If just blank implementation is provided then no filling will be performed.

Parameters:
entListener - - entry point to pass the data for the main fixed dictionary

localFeedInit

boolean localFeedInit(Document document)
This method marks the start of the current document processing by the KIMGazetteer. It allows the implementation to perform any document specific preparations and also feed caching activities.

Parameters:
document - - reference to the document which the gazetteer starts processing.
Returns:
true - if supports local dictionary data; false - usage of local dictionaries is disabled;

localFeedNeeded

void localFeedNeeded(Document document,
                     DictionaryFeeder.ANLList anlList,
                     DictionaryFeeder.EntityListener entListener)
This method will be called by the KIMGazetteer's parser. It will be called after the current parsing step is done, but before a look-up is performed in the local dictionary.

Parameters:
document - - reference to the document being processed. This is passed as a reference to the local feeding session in the feeder implementation.
anlList - - this list represent the current state of the parsing mechanism. It should be used to reduce the amount of data that the feeder will deliver
entListener - - entry point to pass the data for the local dictionary

localFeedEnd

void localFeedEnd(Document document)
This method marks the end of the current document processing by the KIMGazetteer. It allows the implementation to perform any clean-up activities.

Parameters:
document - - reference to the processed document
